{"tid":1896361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍德宮8天7夜南巡遶境起馬 祈求台灣平安、疫情漸緩","createTime":"2020-02-25T05:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T05:47:36.000Z","uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"627413f91001373508c413a8f36076e3b3beab34","tid":1896361,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"桃園市長鄭文燦22日晚間前往蘆竹區龍德宮，出席「桃園龍德宮庚子（109）年南巡祈安遶境起馬活動」。鄭文燦表示，22日晚間起馬晚會開鑼，代表龍德宮四媽祖南巡謁祖遶境活動正式起跑，首先祈求桃園龍德宮8天7夜的遶境活動一路平安、感應萬千，亦祈求台灣平安度過此次肺炎疫情，加快經濟復甦腳步，並祝福龍德宮109年建廟圓滿成功、四媽祖安座順利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0PmgMpY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PmgMpY.jpg&h=e97e8e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h2tV1Yv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2tV1Yv.jpg&h=09a75673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭文燦說，桃園龍德宮每年8天7夜徒步抵達雲林祖廟麥寮拱範宮謁祖，已邁入第15年，活動規模一年比一年盛大，是北台灣重要宗教盛事。109年遶境活動自22日起一連8天，將行經5大縣市、7座宮廟為民祈福，遶境路線約448公里，沿途行經新竹竹蓮寺、後龍慈雲宮、清水紫雲巖、鹿港天后宮，回程經大雅永興宮、苗栗天后宮、湖口顯聖宮，再回到桃園龍德宮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tyenews.com/2020/02/49787/?fbclid=IwAR2rtMMtcg0HvWPjeLpbzlwu08DaEjj2QkfymFgPQhN4oC89zp_ViS7ExDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftyenews.com%2F2020%2F02%2F49787%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2rtMMtcg0HvWPjeLpbzlwu08DaEjj2QkfymFgPQhN4oC89zp_ViS7ExDc&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=20f6e61b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tyenews.com/2020/02/49787/?fbclid=IwAR2rtMMtcg0HvWPjeLpbzlwu08DaEjj2QkfymFgPQhN4oC89zp_ViS7ExDc</a>"},{"pid":"abecb6e36471f58d8052acabc7d8daf9930bebad","tid":1896361,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"香港人行山，台灣人祈福"}]}